OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FHave you noticed how dry and settled
OL,7,Fit's been recently?
OL,9,FThere's a reason for that: a
OL,10,Fpersistent area of high pressure
OL,11,Fthat's been "stuck" over us for nearly
OL,12,Ftwo weeks.
OL,14,FOn the upside, there are a few people
OL,15,Fwho don't enjoy warm, sunny weather.
OL,16,FOn the downside, there has been a
OL,17,Fnoticeable lack of April showers - and
OL,18,Fthat lack of rain is now starting to
OL,19,Fbecome a concerning feature of spring
OL,20,F2026, despite coming into the season
OL,21,Foff a wetter-than-average winter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
