OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FThis "blocked", unvaried weather
OL,7,Fpattern has a name - the omega block -
OL,8,Fand it has the potential to have a
OL,9,Fhuge impact on our weather.
OL,11,FWhat is an omega block and why is it
OL,12,Fcalled that?
OL,14,FAn omega block is the name that
OL,15,Fforecasters use to describe a large,
OL,16,Fstatic area of high pressure with an
OL,17,Farea of low pressure sitting either
OL,18,Fside of it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
