OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FRemember that the jet stream is a fast-
OL,7,Fmoving ribbon of air high in the
OL,8,Fatmosphere that usually flows from
OL,9,Fwest to east across the Atlantic,
OL,10,Facting like a conveyor belt for
OL,11,Fweather systems, guiding rain-bearing
OL,12,Ffrontal systems across the UK.
OL,14,FThe jet stream is usually fairly
OL,15,Fstraight, which gives the UK typically
OL,16,Fchangeable weather with fronts moving
OL,17,Fthrough every few days, bringing a mix
OL,18,Fof sunshine, cloud, and rain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
