OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHowever, sometimes the jet stream
OL,12,Fstarts to wobble into large waves, and
OL,13,Finstead of a smooth flow, it develops
OL,14,Fbig north`south bends: a ridge (bulge
OL,15,Fnorthward) forms, creating a dominant
OL,16,Farea of high pressure and two troughs
OL,17,Fon either side (southward dips)
OL,18,Fforming two areas of low pressure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
