OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777406752
OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FIf these waves become extreme enough,
OL,7,Fthe jet stream can effectively
OL,8,F"freeze" in place. That's when an
OL,9,Fomega block forms - so called because
OL,10,Fit resembles the shape of the omega
OL,11,Fletter  in the Greek Alphabet.
OL,13,FNow you have a situation where,
OL,14,Finstead of rain-bearing frontal
OL,15,Fsystems flowing across the UK, these
OL,16,Fsystems have to travel up and over,
OL,17,Ffollowing the bend in the jet stream.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@HO]sD@HOp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
