OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777406752
OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FThe set-up that we have at the moment
OL,7,F- with high pressure stuck across the
OL,8,FUK - is keeping rain away and, in some
OL,9,Finstances, can allow weeks of heat to
OL,10,Fbuild up, leading to extreme
OL,11,Ftemperatures and large-scale droughts.
OL,13,FHow often do we get them?
OL,15,FOmega blocks can technically form
OL,16,Fanywhere the jet stream exists, but
OL,17,Fthey are most frequent in the mid-
OL,18,Flatitudes where the jet stream is most
OL,19,Factive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
