FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777406752
OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FThe UK might typically experience one
OL,7,Fto three noticeable omega blocks per
OL,8,Fyear, lasting from several days to a
OL,9,Fcouple of weeks.
OL,11,FThey can happen any time of year.
OL,13,FDoes it always give us dry, sunny,
OL,14,Fwarm weather?
OL,16,FNo - it very much depends on the
OL,17,Fposition of where the area of high
OL,18,Fpressure gets "stuck" and also what
OL,19,Ftime of year the block happens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
