OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777406752
OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FIn the summer, an omega high overhead
OL,7,Fis often linked to prolonged heat and
OL,8,Fdry spells, whereas in the winter,
OL,9,Fthis pattern can lock in cold spells
OL,10,For keep storm tracks stuck in place,
OL,11,Fleading to persistent rain and
OL,12,Fflooding.
OL,14,FSome recent examples of how an omega
OL,15,Fhigh can create large-scale weather
OL,16,Fevents:
OL,18,FOne of the clearest modern omega
OL,19,Fblocks set up over northern Europe in
OL,20,Fsummer 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
