OL,3,CWhere are all the April showers and
OL,4,Cwhy is the 'omega block' to blame?
OL,6,FIn some cases, omega blocks create
OL,7,Fsharp contrasts.
OL,9,FHere, the omega high sat over one
OL,10,Fregion, giving extended drought, while
OL,11,Fthe low pressure nearby saw prolonged
OL,12,Frain and flooding; a classic example
OL,13,Fof how this blocked type of pattern
OL,14,Fcan produce opposite extremes at the
OL,15,Fsame time.
OL,17,FHow long will this omega block last?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
